'''''Preethsod Thappa''''' ({{lang-en|Is it wrong to fall in love ?|italic=yes}}) is a 1998 Indian [[Kannada language]] romance-drama musical film directed by [[V. Ravichandran]] and produced by [[Rockline Venkatesh]]. The film stars [[V. Ravichandran]] and [[Shilpa Shetty]] in the lead roles.<ref>[http://entertainment.oneindia.in/kannada/movies/preethsod-thappa/cast-crew.html Cast & Crew]</ref> Actors [[Lokesh]] and [[Lakshmi (actress)|Lakshmi]] and [[Prakash Raj]] feature in other prominent roles. The film is a remake of [[Telugu language|Telugu]] blockbuster film ''[[Ninne Pelladata]]'' (1996) starring [[Akkineni Nagarjuna]] and [[Tabu (actress)|Tabu]] in the lead roles.<ref>http://www.rediff.com/movies/1999/jan/23rem.htm</ref>

The film released on 6 November 1998 across Karnataka cinema halls and was declared a musical blockbuster with all the songs tuned by [[Hamsalekha]] receiving exceptionally well.

