== Soundtrack ==
All the songs are composed and written by [[Hamsalekha]].<ref>[http://mio.to/album/31-kannada_movie_songs/22233-O_Nanna_Nalle__2000_/#/album/31-kannada_movie_songs/22233-O_Nanna_Nalle__2000_/ O Nanna Nalle songs]</ref> This was the last film with Hamsalekha - Ravichandran combination before they parted ways due to the differences in opinion.<ref>[http://crazystarravichandran.webs.com/aboutme.htm About Me- Crazy Star V. Ravichandran] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407092227/http://crazystarravichandran.webs.com/aboutme.htm |date=7 April 2014 }}</ref>

The sound tracks are hugely popular.
Audio copyrights taken By Magnasound India Pvt Ltd.
Cassettes and audio CD's were sold in large numbers.

